{"tid":2454743,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 中國100年前想殖民巴西？","createTime":"2021-03-20T12:47:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T11:10:14.000Z","uid":301152,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"d404be03189f326c17a05a429128d9b85e00d7bf","tid":2454743,"uid":301152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T12:47:06.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\">蘋果日報 x 楊穎宇博士</p><br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"x-large\"><p class=\"center\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 這才是真正的香港史 <br />\n<br />\n</p></span></span><br />\n新一集出咗喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/G4ZAm2aSGiU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FG4ZAm2aSGiU&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDM5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=632bcaa7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/G4ZAm2aSGiU</a><br />\n每集內容都生動有趣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今集流暢度明顯改善咗好多<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 快d click 入去支持啦<br />\n大家要將真正的香港歷史傳承下去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n楊博士加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來香港教科書冇直接用殖民地<br />\n去形容97前的香港 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HhdKYq2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHhdKYq2.png&h=b53fbbfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <span class=\"limegreen\">中國從未承認香港為殖民地</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/46iOFEU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F46iOFEU.png&h=d7e93226&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3f79471528e90ece3cff8a7e11c355e59bcd8e9","tid":2454743,"uid":301152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-0